    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075020/extras/9198bc64b038f8601ca32b7f2cf9bb16.avif?t=1766088657\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;It's On The Mouse&quot; is a Café Management game with a Platforming twist! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump and run around the tables to help Holly welcome her customers and serve them the right orders!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075020/extras/585714c4e1033727106f6a201eb431a8.poster.avif?t=1766088657\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075020/extras/585714c4e1033727106f6a201eb431a8.webm?t=1766088657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075020/extras/585714c4e1033727106f6a201eb431a8.mp4?t=1766088657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prove yourself to be a great tiny maid to unlock new stages, each new stage adding something new to the game, including: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > New Items, customers and even obstacles with unique mechanics to test your maid skills </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlockable characters with their own skills and playstyle, including the adorable little Vtuber guests Ellie Minibot and FairyDuni </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Not all stages are serving stages! Be careful as dangerous bosses will try their best to force little Holly to close her café! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you're tired of serving tables, don't worry as the unlockables will be there to offer you a well deserved break, including a minigame fitting a mouse! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All this and more awaits you in the game, so come visit Holly's café! And don't worry, the fun is on the mouse!</p>",
